      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions match ASTM F1717 protocol; however only a single loading rate (5 mm/min) and single environmental condition (ambient, dry) were evaluated.",
      "rationale": "ASTM F1717 protocol followed for load application and fixation. Only one test condition (ambient, 5 mm/min) was used; physiological saline and body-temperature conditions were not evaluated. This factor is below required level and is noted as a gap; the gap is accepted given the scope of the COU (static structural demonstration, not fatigue or in vivo simulation)."
